Ne poznam ga, on pa mene ne.

00:04:28.689 --> 00:04:30.396
Punca si, on pa fant.

00:04:31.149 --> 00:04:34.733
Vajini deli grejo skupaj.
–Nehaj. O bog.

00:04:34.903 --> 00:04:38.687
Prav, Liz.
Se vidiva v ponedeljek.

00:04:39.533 --> 00:04:43.661
Domov moram.
–Pojdi. –Prav.

