Stran morate. Greva.

00:15:48.871 --> 00:15:51.707
<i>Nekateri so bili
imuni proti virusu.</i>

00:15:52.960 --> 00:15:56.874
<i>Nekateri so
bolezen preboleli.</i>

00:16:00.009 --> 00:16:01.384
<i>Večina pa ne.</i>

