00:22:19.597 --> 00:22:21.507
Stran vas bomo spravili.

00:22:23.852 --> 00:22:25.050
ZDA!

00:22:25.354 --> 00:22:28.688
Pripravljeni moramo biti.
Pri sestri ostani, Sam.

00:22:29.232 --> 00:22:31.439
Gremo.

00:22:32.778 --> 00:22:36.561
Odrasli, pridite
v menzo na sestanek.

00:22:36.740 --> 00:22:40.441
Otroci, pojdite na avtobuse.

00:22:42.203 --> 00:22:43.532
Pridni bodite.

00:22:43.705 --> 00:22:46.623
Odrasli, prosim,
pridite v menzo na posvet.

00:22:47.084 --> 00:22:50.038
Imajo elektriko,
če vozila delajo? –Ne vem.

